{"tid":1285592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特首辦稱林鄭月娥將安排時間見曾示威年輕人等不同人士","createTime":"2019-07-04T15:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T15:44:00.000Z","uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4f59dbbb700c8f04dc3312f1af9e9c060b17c36","tid":1285592,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"特首辦表示，行政長官林鄭月娥將會安排更多時間，親自會見不同黨派、不同階層、不同背景的人士，近日開始邀請不同背景的年輕人見面，當中包括大學生、一些曾參與近期示威活動的年輕人等，聆聽他們的心聲。特首辦回覆查詢時說，會面目的是要深入聆聽、坦誠交流，因此行政長官希望會面以小範圍、閉門形式進行，會面安排亦不會公布。對於科大學生會表明不接受閉門會面，並表示對話的基礎是必須回應反修例示威者的5大訴求，特首辦表示，留意到科大學生會的回應，但希望對方可以再作考慮。<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-04 22:55:19"},{"pid":"d062a748ea77053006e109a965d547ec45be53d9","tid":1285592,"uid":48993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"躝啦，傾你老母，冇嘢想同你傾呀"},{"pid":"c3dca70d9ea6b4e3df5b65976d944a20d3370002","tid":1285592,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/maBZq9V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmaBZq9V.jpg&h=f3e586d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85e92214963cdd66a25c0e9432de254bdba8710e","tid":1285592,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29d7203f6a41a62d8f7416619e8bd0179fbb9a49","tid":1285592,"uid":90601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:43:14.000Z","msg":"戰績:<br />\n777見完利東街抗爭者 我方全滅<br />\n777見完天星碼頭抗爭者 